&gt;&gt; Hydrangea quercifolia or oak-leaf hydrangea.

2
00:00:04,785 --> 00:00:06,900
This is named oak-leaf because of

3
00:00:06,900 --> 00:00:11,745
its lobed leaves which distinctly give an oak-like appearance.

4
00:00:11,744 --> 00:00:15,509
This blooms earliest of the hydrangeas in June, July,

5
00:00:15,509 --> 00:00:18,704
white flowers. Its a large, rangy shrub,

6
00:00:18,704 --> 00:00:22,154
opposite leaves, and lobed leaves.

7
00:00:22,155 --> 00:00:25,870
Hydrangea quercifolia, oak-leaf hydrangea.

